      "writtenOn": "2021-03-31T13:46:27Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Hmm... seems like a shame to have Chrome on Windows still inline, actually, if we think it\u0027s not going to benefit (because it\u0027s only in ES mode as a wrapper around the real driver). That wasn\u0027t my intent.\n\nIs there a better check for this case? Or should I just add more comments?",
